{"type":null,"faqId":44469,"title":"如果是MTP驱动导致无法连接怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.29166666in;margin-left:1.0006944in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.27708334in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>用户可以通过“计算机 &gt; 鼠标右击 &gt; 管理 &gt; 设备管理器”进行查看，正常情况下在设备列表中会比较便携设备字样，电脑会显示出与电脑连接的手机设备信息。如果是MTP驱动问题，则在设备列表中会出现黄色感叹号/便携设备中无法正确读取手机设备信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>点击便携设备（如下有两种异常驱动挂载）</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159289\" style=\"width:5.748611in;height:4.1041665in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159290\" style=\"width:5.764583in;height:4.175in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>右击“便携设备 &gt; 手机设备 &gt; 更新驱动程序软件（P）”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159291\" style=\"width:5.763889in;height:4.1215277in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>点击“浏览计算机以查找驱动程序软件（R）”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159292\" style=\"width:4.8145833in;height:3.7833333in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>从计算机的设备驱动程序列表中选择（L）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159293\" style=\"width:4.80625in;height:3.725in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5.  </span><span>去勾选[显示兼容硬件]，并选择[标准 MTP 设备]  &gt; [MTP USB 设备] &gt; 点击[下一步]。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159294\" style=\"width:5.227778in;height:4.0868053in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">6.  </span><span>完成驱动更新。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159295\" style=\"width:4.945139in;height:3.8159723in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":140,"faqType":"存储与文件管理","useful":2,"unUseful":13,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9969","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Storage-File-management","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400808000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":624,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"未识别设备,连接失败","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}